ZH: 我们公司的员工必须按照轮值制度来上班。
EN: Employees in our company must follow a shift system to work.
ZH: 今天轮到你轮值值班吗？
EN: Is it your turn to be on duty today?
ZH: 老师轮值进行考试监考。
EN: The teacher takes turns to invigilate exams.
